*No Use - in url for uuid!!*
*spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto = CREATE

1-*Patients Get All Specializations :
https://localhost:9443/patients/appointments/specializations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2-*Patients Get The Selected Specialization And See Free Times(Schedule) Of That Specialization :
https://localhost:9443/patients/appointments/specializations/5d9d63c8-cdd1-402c-8ee3-0d378e0d4179
 {
        "scheduleUuid": "ed983625-7ca9-4699-b805-b7e737accc4c",
        "doctorId": "39e25051-29b9-4338-9642-1820d4103727",
        "doctorFirstName": "john",
        "doctorLastName": "smith",
        "startDateTime": "2025-08-25T13:00:00",
        "endDateTime": "2025-08-25T13:30:00",
        "appointmentDurationMin": 30,
        "deleted": false,
        "isBooked": false
    } => Select An Schedule-Id And Add To Patient Body To Post Patient(These Schedules Are Free(isBooked=false))
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3-*Patient Select ScheduleId And Post The Appointment (Appointment-App can be off it works by kafka*):
https://localhost:9443/patients/appointments/save
{
    "scheduleId": "932765e5-f2e8-4727-80ab-417ae7c183ff",
